1. Configure

1a. Generate Twitter API Keys and Tokens

Visit this page and follow these instructions

1b. Create .env file

Create a .env file in the root of your project and add your keys and token

TWITTER_CONSUMER_KEY = <add here>
TWITTER_CONSUMER_SECRET = <add here>
TWITTER_BEARER_TOKEN = <add here>

2. Scripts

2a. Random retweeter

Edit the tweet_id in random-replier.js

Run the script from your terminal:

node random-replier.js

2b. Random retweeter

Edit the tweet_id in random-retweeter.js

Run the script from your terminal:

node random-retweeter.js
